title: New Horizons Sees Gargantuan Canyons on Pluto's Moon Charon - newsR
text: Remember when NASA's New Horizons probe flew by dwarf planet Pluto and its moons back in July? Well, the spacecraft has delivered yet another set of images it obtained during the historic encounter.
